{
  "stem": "27443.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after a while, we were working there, and the hunger was so great in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have what to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, they made selections.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They eliminated people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they made selections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They put you in a line, and whoever looked frail, or whatever, not able to work, they took them out from the ghetto and loaded up on a truck.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That means that they went to their death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't know at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No news was coming back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We thought maybe they go to be resettled somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't realize at that time so much cruelty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew of beatings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't know yet of being gassed or put to death in such a way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew of shooting or beating up, which went on constantly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we didn't know yet the real things to what came later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rejowiec.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Selections went on constantly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there was-- at a certain time, I had typhoid in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Germans were terribly afraid when somebody was sick on typhoid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they surrounded the buildings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They surrounded the sick people, and they-- or they shoot them in that pit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or they loaded them up, as sick as they were, on trucks, to different pits.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I-- when I was sick on the typhoid, the leader from the sugar factory that I worked, he told me once that he had a daughter that he lost, my age.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he kind of felt sorry when I had typhoid, and I couldn't go a few days to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
